                </p>
                <P>
                    <a href="#" class="BookHotelBtn"> BOOK A HOTEL TODAY!! </a>
                </P>
                <div class="text"> <p style="font-weight:1000; font-style:italic; color:black; margin-top:-70px;"> Soreng - Sikkim </p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


